text: Tito Tolin (born 28 October 1935) is an Italian ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Italian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Italy Category:Ski jumpers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
